            fill-opacity="0.62"></path>
        </svg>
      </span>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">The Art of Eight Limbs</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl mt-2">Strength, Precision, Honor.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
    <div class="pt-4">
      <Image
        class="w-full object-fit object-center"
        src={muay_1}
        alt="Strike Force and Fitness"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">What is Muay Thai?</h2>
        <p>
          Muay Thai, often referred to as "The Art of Eight Limbs", is a
          traditional martial art and combat sport from Thailand. It
          distinguishes itself from other martial arts by utilizing punches,
          kicks, elbows, and knee strikes, making it effective for both stand-up
          striking and clinch fighting. Muay Thai is known for its rigorous
          training, physical conditioning, and its deep-rooted cultural and
          spiritual traditions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Why Practice -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 pt-20">
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image
            class="w-full object-fit object-center"
            src={muay_2}
            alt="Strike Force and Fitness"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold my-6">Why Practice Muay Thai?</h2>
          <ul class="list-none">
            <li class="my-2">
              <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300"
                >Dynamic Striking:</span
              >
               Master punches, kicks, elbows, and knee strikes for a versatile
              fighting repertoire.
            </li>
            <li class="my-2">
              <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300"
                >Physical Fitness:</span
              >
               Sculpt your body with intensive workouts that improve stamina,
              flexibility, and strength.
            </li>
            <li class="my-2">
              <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300"
                >Mental Fortitude:</span
              >
               Sharpen your focus, discipline, and determination with every
              training session.
            </li>
            <li class="my-2">
              <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300"
                >Cultural Experience:</span
              > Delve deep into Thai traditions, rituals, and the rich history
              of this ancient sport.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">FAQ</h2>
        <FrequentlyAsked faqs={muayThaiFAQs} client:visible />
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-40 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Step Into the Ring with Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Experience the power, agility, and tradition of Muay Thai. Whether
          you're a novice or a seasoned fighter, our doors are open to all.
        </p>
        <a href="/schedule">
          <Button variant="outline">View Class Schedule</Button></a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
